description:
i love this beat forever. it's very special to me. i love the summery vibe it has and i am so thankful to be able to share it with the world. 
I created this in Ableton with a vocal sample chop from fantasia. I played the bass, crafted the drums, and made all the horns and bells. i have waited to show this to people for a while so if you pick some editions up, send me a dm on twitter so i can get you on the list for future releases and send you the audio file to keep. thank you for listening.
